----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Fixed => non-manipulable
Light => manipulable
Heavy => non-manipulable
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Operators:
Move-Box
Move-Into-Blank-Space
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Rules:
Moving a box:   (is ?box light)
		(adjacent ?x ?box)
		(is (?x patch-ahead-x2) empty) 
		(adjacent (?x patch-ahead-x2) (2-opposite-potential-positions)) 
		=> Pushable 

Moving: 
		(is empty patch)(is patch adjacent) => Moveable

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Optional:
Forklift - required if box is too heavy, will break light boxes.
Ice -   Boxes pushed onto ice slide to the end of the ice patch.
	Worker standing on a patch of ice cannot push.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
